ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 228, Newfoundland and Labrador 2020 Winter Storm
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 228 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of NEWFOUNDLAND and LABRADOR, with respect to the winter storm that occurred from January 17 to 18, 2020.
